data.name: PropertySetInfoChangeEvent
desc: gets delivered whenever an XPropertySetInfo is changed.
A PropertySetInfoChangeEvent object is sent to XPropertySetInfoChangeListeners.

items.name: Handle
lines: contains the implementation handle for the property.
May be -1 if the implementation has no handle.

items.name: Name
lines: contains the name of the property.

items.name: Reason
lines: contains the reason for the event.
